    "en": {
      "title": "Denmark and Sweden ease travel restrictions",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Two European countries have decided to ease travel restrictions to Sri Lanka.",
        "According to the Sri Lanka Association of Inbound Tour Operators, Denmark and Sweden have decided to ease their travel restrictions to Sri Lanka.",
        "Earlier, France, Switzerland, Norway and the UK relaxed the advisories issued to their tourists allowing more tourists to come to Sri Lanka, and the SLTDA welcomed the efforts."
      ],
